 Specifies the name of the configuration file.  The default is
-\fI@sysconfdir@/etc/grossd.conf\fP
+\fI@sysconfdir@/grossd.conf\fP
 .IP "\fB\-h\fP" 4
 Output short usage information and exit.
 .IP "\fB\-n\fP" 4
